
### Grammy


Sauce:
* 1/2 cup tomato sauce
* 2 T mustard
* 2 T vinegar
* 2 T brown sugar
* 1 C water

Loaf:
* 1/2 C tomato sauce
* 1.5 lb ground meat
* 1 C breadcrumbs [or crushed saltines]
* 1 onion, chopped
* 1/4 t pepper
* 1.5 t salt
1 egg, beaten

* mix both well
* pour sauce over loaf
* bake at 350 for 1.5 hours
* baste periodically



### Perini p. 95

* 2 lb lean ground round or chuck
* 1 large baking potato, grated
* 1 medium onion, chopper
* 1-2 cloves garlic
* 2 C chopped fresh tomatoes or 1 16-oz can tomatoes, drained and chopped
* 1 bell pepper
* 1 jalapeno, seeded and chopped
* 2 t prepared mustard or 1 t dry mustard
* 1 T Worcestershire
* 1 t salt
* 1/2 t pepper
* 1 egg, beaten
* 3-4 T picante sauce or tomato sauce

Mix all ingredients except bbq sauce in a large bowl
* top with picante sauce
* bake at 350 for 1 hour

